Tayor Steele's classic surfing video The Show has Greg Browning as a lost space traveler, Chris Malloy as a cowboy, Shane Dorian and Taylor Knox as street thugs, Rob Machado as the Godfather? Sounds more like a night at the local multiplex than one of the greatest surf films of all time. The Show is the first Poor Specimen film to incorporate skits that segue into surfing.
